{"word":"προφθάνω","slug":"προφθάνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προφθάνω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-φθάσω</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-φθήσομαι</el>) (aor1 <el>-έφθᾰσα</el>) (aor2 <el>προὔφθην</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to outrun, anticipate</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to be beforehand</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}